query:
SELECT 
  sea.id as answer_id,
  sea.attemptId,
  sea.questionNumber,
  sea.studentAnswer,
  sea.isCorrect,
  seat.studentId,
  seat.exerciseId,
  se.title as exercise_title
FROM student_exercise_answers sea
LEFT JOIN student_exercise_attempts seat ON sea.attemptId = seat.id
LEFT JOIN student_exercises se ON seat.exerciseId = se.id
LIMIT 10;
